            the selling business and are the lowest ranked cogs. the Sellbot Headquarters is 
            the home of the Sellbots and is most likely the first headquarters a toon will visit.
            the head of all sellbots is tde Senior V.P., which toons can battle in Sellbot HQ.
        </p>
